{
  "chapter": 166,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙一行人逃亡三日三夜，战马疲乏不堪，赵致的马倒地不起。乌达身受重伤，神智迷糊。纪嫣然辨认出前方为秦岭太白山，指出他们偏离原定路线百余里。项少龙与纪嫣然商议对策，纪嫣然分析白飞可能水陆并进追击。项少龙受\"伐木造筏\"启发，设下伏兵之计。众人在河岸设伏，以巨藤拦河，先在对岸疏林故弄玄虚吸引敌人注意。敌人果然水陆两路攻来，木筏撞上巨藤，筏上敌兵纷纷落水，项少龙等弩箭齐发，大破敌军。乌光、乌德在下游成功钩取四条木筏，众人乘筏顺流而下，一夜走完三日路程。抵达秦岭后弃筏登岸，再设伏击。敌人乘七条残破木筏追来，撞上横搁河心的弃筏，乱成一团，项少龙等弩箭伏击，敌军溃败。四日追杀至此告一段落。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_shan",
      "speaker_name": "荆善",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "依尘头来看，敌人仍在五里之外，速度减缓下来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_shan",
      "speaker_name": "荆善",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "真气死人了，我们已经以种种手法布置蛊惑他们，但均被白飞那混蛋识破，没有上当。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "乌达全身发热，神智迷糊，若再颠簸赶路，我怕他会捱不到秦岭。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "若我没有猜错，那该是秦岭第一高峰太白山，照这么看，我们往东偏离原本路线近百多里，难怪没有追上滕二哥。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "听说太白山上有神泉，温度可用来煮食，又可疗伤生肌，若能到那里去，乌达或有希望。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "那是温泉水，泉水吸收了死火山岩浆的热力，又含有大量的矿物质，故有神奇功效。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "什么是'死火山'和'矿物质'？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "迟些再给你解说，当今首务，是要设法逃到秦岭去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "假若嫣然是白飞，看到这么交通方便的一条河，会有什么主意？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "当然怕你伐木造筏，顺河溜掉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "那你会怎办呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我会双管齐下，一方面派人趁夜色摸黑过来，另一方面亦伐木造筏，好能以最快方法赶过来，假如先一步赶抵前方，我们将陷于前虎后狼、插翼难飞之局。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "嫣然伐木为筏的一句话，可使我今晚稳操胜券。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你真要造筏逃生吗？只是这里林木稀疏，要造几条可载这么多人马的筏子，没有整晚工夫休想完成，那时敌人早来哩！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "我们不是'心有灵犀一点通'吗？怎么纪才女今趟竟猜不中为夫的心意呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "心有灵犀一点通，还有什么情话比这更令人着迷呢？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_de",
      "speaker_name": "乌德",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "钩到四条筏子，可以走哩！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这一招'克敌借筏'之计，只有项郎才可以想出来，今趟除非白飞真的会飞，否则休想再追上我们。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "别忘了他们仍有近十条木筏，不过若以每筏十五人计，他们最多只有百多人继续追来，幸好我们无一人不是能以一挡十之辈，尽管来的全是高手，我们打个折扣以一挡五，又欺他们身疲力倦，就在秦岭处再教训他们一顿，便可趁机好好休养，留点精神欣赏秦岭的冰川，亦一乐也。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "我的才女想着些什么呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我在想假若当年人家不放下矜持，厚颜以身相许，现在仍是闷在大梁，且还要苦念着你，那就惨透了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "那我也惨了，定会被没有纪才女为娇妻这大缺憾折磨终身。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你才不会呢！男人都以事业为重，又天生见一个爱一个的性情，不要哄人家哩！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "这么的想于你没有半点好处，而且我说的全是肺腑之言，别忘记你比我的头颅还要多值一倍的黄金呢！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "杜璧竟是这么一个人，要了人的命还不够，还想辱人之妻，迟些我定要找他算账。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 166,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 200
    }
  ],
